6. `RoomRenderer.jsx` — polygon rendering
7. `SvgCanvas.jsx` — pass `selectedId`
8. `SelectionOverlay.jsx` — room selection
9. `selectHandler.js` — hit testing + delete
10. `Toolbar.jsx` — detect button
11. `Sidebar.jsx` — room list
12. `PropertiesPanel.jsx` — room properties
13. `deserialize.js` — backward compat

## Verification

1. `npx vite build` — no errors
2. Draw 4 walls forming a rectangle → click "Detect Rooms" → room appears with fill, name "Room 1", and area label
3. Draw walls forming 2 adjacent rooms → detect → both rooms appear with correct areas
4. Click a room polygon → selection overlay appears, properties panel shows name/area/color
